summary: Pokemon fans - If you want any of my Pokemon items, send me a message over on Etsy (account: quietsnooze) so we can talk private...
body:
Pokemon fans - If you want any of my Pokemon items, send me a message over on Etsy (account: quietsnooze) so we can talk private listings because all of’m were taken down but I still have to get rid of them somehow! Super clearance cheap! The buttons are a dollar each (five dollars for six buttons) and the whole gift pack is twenty (plus shipping)!

Please help me clear this stuff out! I no longer exhibit at fan conventions to be able to get rid of them otherwise. I’ll be throwing in free Wooloo stickers while supplies last!
